# Example .env for local development
# Copy this file to a file named .env in the project root and fill the keys.
# Do NOT commit your real .env with secret keys to git.

# Stripe API keys (test)
# Copy your real keys into a local file named `.env` (NOT version controlled).
# Example (do NOT commit the actual secret key):
# STRIPE_SECRET_KEY=sk_test_xxx_replace_here
# STRIPE_PUBLIC_KEY=pk_test_xxx_replace_here

